dct_title_s: A map of North America with the European settlements & whatever else is remarkable in ye West Indies from the latest and best observations
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows California as an island. Describes western and northwestern portions of North America as "Parts Unknown." Prime meridian: London. Appears in: Rapin de Thoyras, Paul. The history of England, translated by N. Tindal. London, 1744. v. 3.
dct_publisher_sm: [London : Printed for John and Paul Knapton, 1744]
